{"tid":957634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲乜嘢充滿負能量嘅句子？","createTime":"2018-12-27T07:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T07:36:24.000Z","uid":218353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53764992946cd125ac09a5429de034b7f9795b6b","tid":957634,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"等我拋磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不順利嗎？多照照鏡子，很多事情你就明白原因了。<br />\n<br />\n有時候你會懷疑自己的能力，別擔心，偶爾你是對的，你能力真的有問題。<br />\n<br />\n努力了這麼多年，但凡是有點天賦的，也該有點成功的跡象了。<br />\n<br />\n有一種女仔， 不會要你的車，不會要你的樓， 不會要你的錢， 更不會要你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbee5303015e33ba9667daf9498ed3ff3448e80","tid":957634,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"共享當中國人的榮耀"},{"pid":"4207a32d9a7827f4146bcb8b1ce76c747dc0f84d","tid":957634,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"失敗乃成功之母"},{"pid":"a7930c3ccd57d25431bbb49ba942b9f1abfe005a","tid":957634,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗唔開心,反正聽日都一樣唔開心"}]}